    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Connect All Your Data Sources"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Leverage Automated data integration pipelines built in a low-code environment to connect all your data, eliminating data silos to achieve faster & real-time insights.",
        "Connect your data from 100+ sources, apply data cleaning, transformation, munging and wrangling to shape your data in the desired structure, and load into a target destination to unlock actionable insights and enable reliable & real-time, data-driven decision making."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "Request a call",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ias-featured-img-1.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 557,
          "h": 445
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Building Automated ETL/ELT Pipelines"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Step 01"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Step 03"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Step 02"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Join Us on the Journey Towards Success",
        "Ingest your data from a vast library of 100+ pre-built data connectors and custom API integration capabilities.",
        "Securely load your transformed data into any target destination type such as database, data warehouse, flat file, or tree files.",
        "Carry out data wrangling, massaging, and mapping to transform your data into the desired shape & format"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ias-concept-img-icon-1.webp",
