      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Avoid the need to find and hire additional staff with skills in data engineering and integration as we handle everything for you.",
        "Speedy delivery to start receiving actionable insights.",
        "Scale to consume large volumes of data as your data sources expand with our optimized data modeling techniques",
        "A team of certified experts, ready to support & resolve your performance or downtime issues",
        "We build a customized solution based on your requirements and preferred technology stack."
      ],
